ailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/19\/overeat-hungriest-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25977,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Satiety: Those who overeat are hungriest in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: A man belched in the presence of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cRestrain your belching, for those who were most satiated in the world will be the most hungry on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2478 Grade: Sahih li\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26004,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/04\/aisha-first-trial-overeating\/","url_meta":{"origin":25977,"position":3},"title":"Aisha on Gluttony: First trial among Muslims was eating too much","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 4, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"'Urwah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cVerily, the first trial to occur in this nation after the passing of its Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was people eating to their fill. For when people fill their stomachs, their bodies are fattened, their hearts are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25997,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/02\/prophet-many-nights-hungry\/","url_meta":{"origin":25977,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hunger: The Prophet spent many nights hungr